# Liabilities Loans And Placements Amount

## identifier
de14211

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, for loans which are not evidenced by the issue of debt securities and account balances with institutions not regarded as deposit-taking institutions (placements).

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.LoansAndPlacements.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.26
- period=instant
